room_title: Escape room "The Psych Ward" by Cross Roads Escape Games in Los Angeles
room_address: 4245 E La Palma Ave, Anaheim, CA 92807
room_description: Sane or Insane? Trustworthy or not? These are the questions Dr. Griffin wants you to answer. He has created a social experiment for a select group of patients. Some of these patients he believes are sane, others, completely insane. Like lab rats, he has put you inside his twisted experiment of paranoia and challenges you to figure out who to trust and who to betray.
